@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@rekapBackupUrl = {{baseUrl}}/rekap-backup

### 0. Login & Ambil Token (Jalankan ini Pertama Kali)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Set Variable Token (otomatis diambil dari response login di atas)
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MSwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJhZG1pbiIsInJvbGUiOiJhZG1pbiIsImlhdCI6MTc3ODgxNzYyMCwiZXhwIjoxNzc4OTA0MDIwfQ.m-3DLSXH1xB64A_IAmglAof2mJwml9f_slTIiKunSrc


### =========================================================
### REKAP BACKUP ENDPOINTS (Wajib jalankan login terlebih dulu)
### =========================================================

### 1. Trigger Full Sync JSON dari Database (Admin)
# Endpoint ini akan menyalin data dari database MySQL ke file JSON lokal (Staging)
POST {{rekapBackupUrl}}/staging/sync
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2. Get Summary Data
# Mengambil rangkuman data harian dan bulanan per cabang
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. Get Available Years
# Mengambil rentang tahun (oldest dan newest) dari data staging
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/years
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Get Resume Harian per Cabang
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/harian/resume/G033
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Get Resume Bulanan per Cabang
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/bulanan/resume/G001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Get Detail Logs Harian (dengan Pagination)
# (Parameter: cabang / periode)
# Query Params (opsional): page, limit
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/harian/detail/G001/202401?page=1&limit=25
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7. Get Detail Logs Bulanan (dengan Pagination)
# (Parameter: cabang / periode)
# Query Params (opsional): page, limit
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/bulanan/detail/G001/202401?page=1&limit=25
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 8. Update Note Harian (Live Edit Note)
PATCH {{rekapBackupUrl}}/harian/detail/note
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "cabang": "G001",
  "kdtk": "TB01",
  "periode": "20240101",
  "note": "Catatan tes harian via HTTP"
}

###

### 9. Update Note Bulanan (Live Edit Note)
PATCH {{rekapBackupUrl}}/bulanan/detail/note
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "cabang": "G001",
  "kdtk": "TB01",
  "periode": "202401",
  "note": "Catatan tes bulanan via HTTP"
}

###

### 10. Export Excel Data
# Mengunduh file Excel (Uji coba di browser disarankan untuk format blob)
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/export?cabang=G001&startYear=2024&endYear=2024
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
